{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Petitioners contend that the respective assembly operations conducted by B&L Ireland and B&L Hong Kong were substantial in nature. Respondent disagrees.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
