{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In addition, the sunglasses assembled at both B&L Ireland and B&L Hong Kong were inspected at least once by someone other than the operator who assembled them to ensure that the sunglasses complied with B&L\rquote s quality standards. Dr. Cohen testified that, at least in Ohio, an optician was required to examine prescription eyeglasses before they were distributed to the ultimate consumer. Although the position of an inspector at B&L Ireland and at B&L Hong Kong was not the equivalent of an optician who is licensed and trained to dispense prescription eyeglasses, the record in these cases establishes that inspectors at B&L Ireland and at B&L Hong Kong required significant periods of training and experience in order to perform their jobs properly. The need for trained inspectors to ensure that the sunglasses assembled by B&L Ireland and by B&L Hong Kong met B&L\rquote s quality standards further demonstrates the substantiality of the assembly operations conducted by each of those corporations.
